      <originalsloc id="aspace_09cc8d94ce2733d791c168325a934ee5">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection can be found on microfilm (HM 252) and in the Central American Collection (MS 1779).   This is a collection of correspondence; government documents, including reports, and decrees; church documents; and writings from Central America (Guatemala, Honduras, Nicaragua and Panama) on civil, military, economic, religious, political, linguistic and social topics.</p>  
      </originalsloc>
